title: Edward Gorey Holiday Cards
description:
’Tis the season to be Gorey. . . . This is Edward Gorey at his festive best. Join him as you sip the flaming punch, sample a cookie, dispose of the fruitcake, and decorate the fireplace. Contains five cards of each of the following: "The Great Veiled Bear," “Suppiluliumas dozes while the family finishes decorating the fireplace.,” "Fruitcake," and "Flaming Punch Bowl."
  • Dimensions: Box size: 5.4 x 7.4 x 1.5 in. Card size: 5 x 7 in.
  • Materials: Recycled paper with soy-based inks, high-quality 250 gsm card stock, soft white envelopes
  • Inside message: Season’s Greetings
  • 20 cards w/envelopes
